    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "At least back to pandas 0.12 this already gives this same error.\n\nIf you want to construct a DataFrame from a simple dict, you should have the items as lists, or else provide an index, or convert it a series:\n\n```\nIn [3]: pd.DataFrame({'one': [1], 'two': [2]})\nOut[3]:\n   one  two\n0    1    2\n\nIn [4]: pd.DataFrame({'one': 1, 'two': 2}, index=[0])\nOut[4]:\n   one  two\n0    1    2\n\nIn [5]: pd.Series({'one': 1, 'two': 2})\nOut[5]:\none    1\ntwo    2\ndtype: int64\n```\n"
  },
