    "body": "The documentation should at least be clarified (although I think this is a bug). When using from_dict, there is no way to pass an index, yet the very name of the method suggests that you should be able to pass a dict and get a DataFrame.\n\nPreferably, from_dict makes an index for you. Otherwise, the documentation needs to clearly state the kinds of dicts that are acceptable.\n"
